2. 

In this Order— 

“the Act” means the Electricity Regulation Act, 1999 (No. 23 of 1999) 
as amended by the Water Act; 

“Act of 2013” means the Water Services Act 2013; 

“days” means calendar days; 

“the Commission” means the Commission for Regulation of Utilities 
established under the Act; 

“levy year” means the calendar year to 31st December 2025; 

period” means the period of 3 months ending on 31 March, 30 June, 30 
September or 31 December; 

“the Water Act” means the Water Services (No. 2) Act 2013; 

“the Water Services Acts 2007 to 2013” means the Water Services Acts 
2007 and 2012, the Act of 2013 and the Water Act; 

and any cognate words shall be construed accordingly.
